COPY_EXISTING ~C0D4_5.SPL~ ~OVERRIDE~
SAY NAME1 ~Pact of Nature I~
SAY UNIDENTIFIED_DESC ~Pact of Nature
The avenger may select one of three Pacts of Nature, each providing permanent bonuses and penalties. Each pact may only be selected once.

PACT OF NATURE'S FURY: The avenger's attacks deal one additional unmitigated piercing damage to unnatural creatures such as undead, outsiders and abberations.
   The damage bonus increases to two at 9th level and three at 15th level.
   The avenger loses four points of Dexterity after selecting this Pact.

PACT OF NATURE'S SECRETS: The avenger gains the use of certain arcane spells, and a +1 bonus to casting speed.
   1st level: Chromatic Orb, Spook
   2nd level: Invisibility, Horror
   3rd level: Slow, Vampiric Touch
   4th level: Improved Invisibility, Polymorph Self
   5th level: Chaos, Lower Resistance
   6th level: Flesh to Stone, Wyvern Call
   7th level: Mass Invisibility, Sphere of Chaos
   The casting speed bonus increases to +2 at 9th level and +3 at 15th level.
   The avenger loses four points of Strength after selecting this Pact.

PACT OF NATURE'S HARVEST: The avenger gains a x2 backstab multiplier. Additionally, backstabs made by the avenger entangle the target for up to three rounds. At the end of each round, the target will lose 5% of their current hit points and their resistances, including Magic Resistance, which are transferred to the avenger for one turn. The target may not make a Saving Throw for the first round of entanglement, but may make a Saving Throw vs. Spells at -3 and -1 respectively for the following two rounds to break free and resist the draining effect.
   The avenger's backstab multiplier increases to x3 at 9th level and x4 at 15th level.
   The avenger loses four points of Constitution after selecting this Pact.~

